{"type": "article", "id": 26637, "title": "面包灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070214544291qO7pK8Eow6NJmC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">谁说面包不能成为灯具的灵感来源？设计师 Yicong Lu 的这款“面包灯”看上去就像是一个烤面包机，插槽中的“面包片”充当了灯泡的角色。虽然并没有设计专门的调光器，但只要上下调整“面包片”的高度即可改变灯光的亮度，既生动又充满了科技感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145439J52pzNkFYqbdnli6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021454407GhqcFrOK8QYXuoB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145440BwMZrNYx01PsjuAn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145442YIMlTw26oORU0rEH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n"}